"AAM6070TPB2", "REV: 1.01", and "PCB MADE IN CHINA" appears :to be silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos.
There is a BCM3341 (BCM6341?) on board. FCC photos appear to show :the device with 2x ''Samsung'' K4S281632-TC75 (16MB RAM, 32MB total).
Default settings in the FCC manual (likely wrong.. or pre-release) are... *IP: 192.168.1.1 *Login/pass: admin/admin *SSID: '''Broadcom'''
